Time Series Forecast Project - Sales Forecasting using ARIMA
Overview:
This project focuses on time series analysis and forecasting of sales data using the ARIMA model.
The goal is to analyze historical sales trends and predict future sales values.

Technologies Used:
Python
Pandas
Matplotlib
Statsmodels (ARIMA)
Scikit-learn

Dataset:
File: train.csv
Contains sales transaction data with Order Date and Sales

Project Workflow:
  Data Loading & Exploration
      Loaded dataset using Pandas
      Checked structure using .head() and .info()
  Data Preprocessing
      Converted Order Date to datetime format
      Sorted data chronologically
      Checked for duplicate values
  Time Series Transformation
      Aggregated daily sales
      Converted data into monthly sales trends
  Data Visualization
      Plotted monthly sales trend using Matplotlib
  Model Building (ARIMA)
      Split data into train and test sets
      Applied ARIMA model (1,1,1)
      Forecasted future sales
  Model Evaluation
      Evaluated using Mean Absolute Error (MAE)

Results:
    Successfully forecasted sales for the next 6 months
    Model performance evaluated using MAE
